videos.headline: Mackenzie Holmes rolls hard to the basket for the finish
videos.description: Grace Berger finds Mackenzie Holmes rolling to the basket with a nice pass for an easy bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Mackenzie Holmes rolls hard to the basket for the finish) 2023/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moira Joiner knocks down a quick three for the Spartans
videos.description: DeeDee Hagemann finds Moira Joiner for a quick three to put the Spartans up double-digits.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Moira Joiner knocks down a quick three for the Spartans) 2023/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kamaria McDaniel dimes Moira Joiner for a corner 3
videos.description: Kamaria McDaniel shows off her handles with a nice crossover and hits Moira Joiner with a jump pass for an open corner three.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kamaria McDaniel dimes Moira Joiner for a corner 3) 2023/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kamaria McDaniel knocks down a tough 3
videos.description: Kamaria McDaniel keeps the Spartans' hot start going with a tough three from downtown.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kamaria McDaniel knocks down a tough 3) 2023/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sara Scalia drains a 3 to cap off a Hoosiers run
videos.description: Sara Scalia caps off a 7-0 Indiana run with a nice three-pointer to cut into the Spartans' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sara Scalia drains a 3 to cap off a Hoosiers run) 2023/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moira Joiner nails another 3 for Michigan State
videos.description: Moira Joiner uses a jab step and pulls up to knock down the Spartans' 8th three-pointer of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Moira Joiner nails another 3 for Michigan State) 2023/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sara Scalia ties it with a wide-open 3
